  "model_name": "item_knn_xsubj_subsim",
  "notes": "Sub 65 \u2014 cross-subject k-NN with subject-similarity reweighting. Retrieves top-K=20 globally (item-text sim) and then reweights each retrieved response by a Gaussian on the |\u03bc(s) - \u03bc(s')| subject-mean-accuracy gap (\u03c3=0.10). Interpolates between sub 33 (within-subject only) and sub 64 (global, no subject identity).",
